<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: sans-serif; background-color: #f3f4f6;">
    <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 20px;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);">
            
            <!-- Header with Logo -->
            <tr>
              <td align="center" style="background-color: #360D0C; padding: 20px;">
                <%= image_tag attachments['logo.svg'].url, alt: 'CocktailScout', style: "width: 150px; height: auto; display: block;" %>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Body Content -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 30px; color: #374151; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">
                <h1 style="color: #360D0C; margin-top: 0; font-size: 24px;">Test Email f√ºr <%= @user.username %></h1>
                
                <p>Dies ist eine Test-Email vom CocktailScout System.</p>
                
                <p>Wenn du diese Nachricht liest, funktioniert der Mail-Versand (und die Styles) korrekt.</p>
                
                <div style="background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; font-family: monospace; color: #333;">
                  Timestamp: <%= Time.current %><br>
                  Environment: <%= Rails.env %>
                </div>

                <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
                  Prost,<br>
                  <strong style="color: #360D0C;">Dein CocktailScout Team</strong>
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            
            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
              <td align="center" style="background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
                &copy; <%= Time.current.year %> CocktailScout. Alle Rechte vorbehalten.
              </td>
            </tr>

          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>